OL,3,CMan guilty of 'poisoning' incident at
OL,4,Csummer camp to be sentenced next year
OL,6,FA man who pleaded guilty to 17
OL,7,Foffences relating to a "poisoning
OL,8,Fincident" at a Leicestershire summer
OL,9,Fcamp will be sentenced next year.
OL,11,FJon Ruben, 76 admitted charges
OL,12,Fincluding eight counts of wilful ill
OL,13,Ftreatment of a child in relation to
OL,14,Feight separate victim, one count of
OL,15,Facquiring or possession of dutiable
OL,16,Fgoods by fraudulent intent and three
OL,17,Fcounts of possession of a class C drug.
