OL,3,CMan guilty of 'poisoning' incident at
OL,4,Csummer camp to be sentenced next year
OL,6,FThe former vet from Ruddington in
OL,7,FNottinghamshire was told he will be
OL,8,Fhanded a "significant" prison sentence
OL,9,Ffor his crimes.
OL,11,FHe also pleaded guilty at a previous
OL,12,Fhearing to three counts of making
OL,13,Findecent photographs of a child, one
OL,14,Fcount of assault by penetration of a
OL,15,Fboy under 13 and one count of sexual
OL,16,Fassault of a boy under 13.
OL,18,FHe previously pleaded not guilty to a
OL,19,Fsecond charge of assault by
OL,20,Fpenetration of a boy under 13.
