OL,6,FAt a hearing at Leicester Crown Court
OL,7,Ftoday, the prosecution changed this
OL,8,Fnot guilty plea to a second charge of
OL,9,Fassault by penetration of a boy under
OL,10,F13.
OL,12,FLeicestershire Police said the plea
OL,13,Fwas accepted following full discussion
OL,14,Fand consultation with the
OL,15,Finvestigation team and the victim's
OL,16,Ffamilies.
