OL,3,CMan guilty of 'poisoning' incident at
OL,4,Csummer camp to be sentenced next year
OL,6,FHis case had been adjourned for
OL,7,Fprosecutors to decide if they would
OL,8,Ftake him to trial over the charge he
OL,9,Fdenied, but Mary Prior KC said "it is
OL,10,Fnot in the public interest" to proceed
OL,11,Fwith it after speaking to the victim's
OL,12,Ffamily and the police.
OL,14,FJudge Timothy Spencer KC told Ruben,
OL,15,Fwho appeared by video-link from HMP
OL,16,FPeterborough, that he will be
OL,17,Fsentenced on February 6 for the
OL,18,Foffences he admitted.
