OL,4,Csummer camp to be sentenced next year
OL,6,FThe judge told Ruben: "A significant
OL,7,Fsentence of imprisonment is coming
OL,8,Fyour way", to which the defendant
OL,9,Freplied: "I understand that."
OL,11,FThe court previously heard that Ruben
OL,12,Fcrushed up and injected drugs into
OL,13,Fsweets and played a "sweet game" with
OL,14,Fchildren at the summer camp.
OL,16,FSeveral young children became ill
OL,17,Fafter playing the game and found it
OL,18,Fdifficult to walk, had slurred speech
OL,19,Fand could not wake up, the plea
OL,20,Fhearing was told.
