OL,6,FSome children "couldn't be roused at
OL,7,Fall" and were vomiting, with one left
OL,8,Funconscious.
OL,10,FThe rented premises, Stathern Lodge,
OL,11,Fin Leicestershire, were not connected
OL,12,Fto the camp itself and Ruben was in
OL,13,Fcharge of a number of young people
OL,14,Fthere.
OL,16,FHe had run a holiday camp for 27
OL,17,Fyears, the previous hearing was told.
