OL,3,CMan guilty of 'poisoning' incident at
OL,4,Csummer camp to be sentenced next year
OL,6,FThe defendant's stepson raised
OL,7,Fconcerns with his partner during the
OL,8,Fcamp after finding baby oil, syringes
OL,9,Fwith white powder in and other items.
OL,11,FEight children were taken to hospital
OL,12,Fafter a report was made to police on
OL,13,FJuly 27, and liquid Xanax was found to
OL,14,Fhave been used on some of the victims.
OL,16,FThe indecent images charges admitted
OL,17,Fby Ruben related to 50 category A
OL,18,Findecent videos of children, 22
OL,19,FCategory B videos and seven Category C
OL,20,Fvideos made between August 2023 and
OL,21,FJune this year.
